(window.webpackJsonp=window.webpackJsonp||[]).push([[40],{299:function(module,exports){module.exports={compilerOutput:[],storyContent:{inkVersion:19,root:[[{"->t->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_sound"},{"->t->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_root"},{"->t->":"yield"},{"->t->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_pumped_options"},{"->t->":"yield"},{"->t->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_insertion_and_deletion"},{"->t->":"yield"},{"->t->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_fucked_options"},{"->t->":"yield"},{"->t->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_finale"},"ev","str","^","/str","/ev",{"->":"done"},["done",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{chapter_12_the_big_payback_sound:['^<stop-sound group="music" name="boardroom-daydream" />',"\n",'^<play-sound group="music" name="alpha-beta-gamma" />',"\n","ev","void","/ev","->->",{"#f":1}],chapter_12_the_big_payback_root:[["^<h5><time>2301.06.14:1730</time></h5>","\n","^<p>","\n","^Today is take your daughter to work day. I have been assigned to the financial services department for my two-week plan, in accordance with my request to assist Father. Time to be a business princess and serve the heretic king of business.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^First is to meditate and fast for a full day. To be a member of a fast-moving team requires tracing the sinews and seismographs of excess value, dense pockets of data invisible but to the most exalted soldiers of fortune. One must be a team player at all times, in every hour, weekendless and singularly-minded, operationalizing and solutionizing at 10x rates, remaining, for every tick of the graph, psychically and morally agile.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^At the end of the period of fasting I eat bread and drink water and I allow a new cryptonym to rise to the tip of my mind.","\n","^</p>","\n",["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_root.0.21.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0",flg:18},{s:["^Quanta Charm.",{"->":"$r",var:!0},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_root.0.22.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1",flg:18},{s:["^Vomma Beran.",{"->":"$r",var:!0},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_root.0.23.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-2",flg:18},{s:["^Copula Scholes.",{"->":"$r",var:!0},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_root.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.21.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev","str","^Quanta Charm","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_cryptonym",re:!0},{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_root.0.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.22.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev","str","^Vomma Beran","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_cryptonym",re:!0},{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-2":["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_root.0.c-2.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.23.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev","str","^Copula Scholes","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_cryptonym",re:!0},{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"g-0":["^<p>","\n","^Yes. Exactly and perfectly so.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Second is the download.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^The Operating Medium selected for today, who will be in a cell down the hall embarking on consciousness-transferrence meditation and sending me his business energies, was an options trader in a past life. He will be the parrot on my shoulder, my eye in the sky, a human calculating engine trained to read the tectonics of price as if they were bones, scrying the sweetmeats and offal of destiny. My gnostic <em>financiomancer</em>.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^I stride across the land of business, a regal heretic.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^In the cell is a bed, a closet, and a Montfleur console, diverted from a storage cabinet or empty desk at some inattentive Antediluvian 500 corporation. The Montfleur has been hacked to hop, in the standard Lamarrian semantic, across millions of precracked legit password hashes.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^The eyes of the Archon will be deployed against His own market. We survey insider data on highly classified, exponential unemployment increases, spurred by energy and real estate index crashes, lit afire by the resurgence of the changing plague.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Jobs data is a week late. If it's not released tomorrow or the day after, the effect will be the same.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^No news is sold like bad news when it comes to the ordinarily punctual heralds and guard towers. That's two weeks, until the investments are guaranteed to move into the money from far outside. Three weeks max. The indices will look less like furious candles than bloody rapiers. A position guaranteed as platinum, paying out like card counting. The perfect financial crime.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n",'^"How. Are. You. Doing. Newbie?" I hear the words without sound, my brain without a body, just down the hallway, and I felt him mouth these formless utterances against my ear. But the link is one-way, and I have no way to reply.',"\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^Here is what I have:","\n","^</p>","\n","^<ul>","\n","^<li>","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^100,000 in seed funding.</li>","\n","^<li>50% margin on a 9% vig. No fees, though.</li>","\n","^<li>A cross-application exploit with fixed correlation offsets on ETAF derivatives, up to a 90% reduction for options, on a highly-leveraged portfolio with maintenance costs of almost nil. I should be able to leverage about 125,000% of the seed funding.</li>","\n","^</ul>","\n","^<p>","\n","^A little bit of envelope math says that's ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^18,750,000 to turn into even more. Scary, yes. But less so when I know how to make all my gambles pay out regardless of how the cards turn.","\n","^</p>","\n",["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_root.0.g-0.90.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-3",flg:18},{s:["^I'll load myself up to the tits on FADE puts.",{"->":"$r",var:!0},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_root.0.g-0.91.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-4",flg:18},{s:["^I'll write 15,000 wildly OTM calls on ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^AXIL.",{"->":"$r",var:!0},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_root.0.g-0.92.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-5",flg:18},{s:["^I'll day-trade ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^XIOV ETAFs.",{"->":"$r",var:!0},null]}],{"c-3":["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_root.0.g-0.c-3.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.90.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^<p>","\n",'^Nobody remembers what "FADE" stood for, or even whether it stood for anything, but everyone knows what it is: an option contract bought against a relatively volatile stock, for a strike price intimidatingly out of the money, for a strike date in a week or less.',"\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^The sort of call or put option that costs little and entices with stratospheric payouts, but only if the stock starts drilling towards ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^0 by EOD.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n",'^The sort that any sensible trader looks at and hears the whole Greek chorus warning, like prodigal Sirens, "on \u0394, on \u0398, on \u0393, on \u03a1, on Vega, turn back!"',"\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^500,000 contracts at ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^20 per contract, a strike price of ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^10 per share \u2014 90% out of the money! \u2014 and a strike date on the next Friday. Comically likely to turn into a vast collection of goose eggs, expiring worthless. But this is an enterprise of faith, not sense, and we know those who hold faith in diamond hands will print.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^Especially when those diamond hands hold a sniper rifle.","\n","^</p>","\n","ev","str","^FADE","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_investment_option",re:!0},{"->":".^.^.^.g-1"},{"#f":5}],"c-4":["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_root.0.g-0.c-4.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.91.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^<p>","\n","^The coolest thing about writing short options is this: I can win (and lose) basically infinite money.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Like a casino where I could lose all the money in my pocket, or turn it into a billion credits. Worst case, five minutes later, the big guys wearing dark sunglasses tell me that I owe them infinite credits now. That's called leverage, that's called a margin call, that's called frisson. That's how I make 10,000% week-over-week gains.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^That's the little death at the heart of every victory, that chance it all turns to shit at the last minute, or starts moving the wrong way from the first. The cheaper I sell them, the more likely to strike in the money \u2014 which is to say to lose almost inestimable amounts \u2014 and the more I'll sell. Like clicking a button that just adds credits to the account every time, but I'll probably die a week later.","\n","^</p>","\n","ev","str","^AXIL","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_investment_option",re:!0},{"->":".^.^.^.g-1"},{"#f":5}],"c-5":["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_root.0.g-0.c-5.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.92.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^<p>","\n","^The ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^XIOV is revered by long option buyers, despised by professional option sellers and retail investors alike. ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev",'^XIOV is nicknamed "the fear index," a measure of volatility in the market. It indicates the degree to which investors expect and are planning for big changes, usually bad.',"\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^One may then, on top of this, trade ETAF stocks pegged to the ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^XIOV, trade futures against it, and trade options against both. The structure recurses towards infinity. The snake remains in pursuit of itself.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^If I know when the structure will shift, when the snake will bite down on itself, I can print credits like manna from thin air.","\n","^</p>","\n","ev","str","^XIOV","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_investment_option",re:!0},{"->":".^.^.^.g-1"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-1":["^<p>","\n","^I just have to be absolutely certain the option won't move away from the strike price.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Good thing we're unconstrained by normal business ethics. We're free to turn whichever dials we please, secure in the knowledge we're ever in search of perfect virtue.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^This is the purpose of our riflemen, grenadiers, and intrusion specialists.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^<em>Nothing</em> moves a stock price like blood on the evening news, with the stock symbol overlaid so professionally overtop, a pretty talking head providing minute-to-minute updates of a corporate-wide, publicly traded death spiral.","\n","^</p>","\n","ev","void","/ev","->->",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],chapter_12_the_big_payback_pumped_options:['^<stop-sound group="music" name="alpha-beta-gamma" />',"\n",'^<play-sound group="music" name="believe-in-the-upside-down" />',"\n","^<p>","\n","^The pump is go. Three tac teams are on standby in lo-vis r-wings, hovering outside Novoebacurum. All are ready to insert. Father just needs to say the word.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n",'^Like a good Father, he is here before he is even asked, his voice filling our chakras with gold: "OPBD is go."',"\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Now the psychic whiplash of one soul descending onto another, a veil.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^The cell is gone, the Montfleur terminal a distant memory, crushed by a rising wave of color, passion, rage, love, the taste of death like bile, teeth grinding teeth to meal, the gustatory rush of martyrs' blood beneath gums and tongue, sweet and umami.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^All these and so much more, twenty-one times over, for a few brilliant and refracted seconds.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^The urge is always to try to control the body which belongs to my eyes, but to do so here is to recall every time the sun rose as paralyzing hypnopomp.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^The sun crests the horizon, the snake whirls, the carbons lattice like honeycomb, dreams climb atop the chest and sit down with all their weight.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^Learning to see without movement, to know without intention, is to be water atop stone, flowing over, under, within.","\n","^</p>","\n","ev","void","/ev","->->",{"#f":1}],chapter_12_the_big_payback_insertion_and_deletion:["^<p>","\n","^The tac teams move in as red teamers, secretaries, delivery men, utility inspectors, SaaS salespeople, and break-in artists. They interfere with numerous sites of financial value. Speculation houses, fishers of value, coder shops, data lakes filled with a trillion byte-sized minnows.","\n","^</p>","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_investment_option"},"/ev",["du","ev","str","^AXIL","/str","==","/ev",{"->":".^.b",c:!0},{b:["pop","\n",{"->t->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_axil_intrusion"},{"->":".^.^.^.13"},null]}],["du","ev","str","^FADE","/str","==","/ev",{"->":".^.b",c:!0},{b:["pop","\n",{"->t->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_fade_intrusion"},{"->":".^.^.^.13"},null]}],["du","ev","str","^XIOV","/str","==","/ev",{"->":".^.b",c:!0},{b:["pop","\n",{"->t->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_xiov_intrusion"},{"->":".^.^.^.13"},null]}],"pop","nop","\n","ev","void","/ev","->->",{"#f":1}],chapter_12_the_big_payback_axil_intrusion:[["^<p>","\n","^I see with Hamish's eyes.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^We hold a briefcase. Inside the briefcase is an incendiary device. When the switch inside the briefcase is turned, it will ignite the charges, spraying flames in a broad arc, burning its primary charge for fifteen full minutes.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^There are fire suppression systems, yes. But what fire suppression system can handle a metal-fluorine fire?","\n","^</p>","\n","ev","str","^Go in through the back window.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0",flg:20},"ev","str","^Walk right into the server room.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1",flg:20},"ev","str","^Have the secretary deliver it.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2",flg:20},{"c-0":["\n","^<p>","\n","^The grapnel pistol fires, a sharp spurt in the humid morning. Unnoticeable in the days of coughing death.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^If someone sees us scaling the back wall, a spider who came in through the parking lot, nothing comes of it.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^In through the office window. Break the VP's neck. Sneak around the cubicles. Force the security guard to open the server room. Tie him up with the grapnel, activate the suitcase, five minute delay, and get the fuck out.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^The rescue hook reaches into the parking lot, fifty KPH and barely missing car windshields. That'd be loud enough to draw attention.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^Salome is an artist of a pilot, though, and we barely feel the speed when we're carried off into the distance.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^Smoke begins to pour from the flat glass facade, burning in the low sunrise.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^It rises lazily and is eclipsed by the horizon.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["\n","^<p>","\n","^A nod at the secretary, approaching the desk but not touching it, six feet distance, masked and smiling with our eyes.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^All the employed Antediluvians have disappeared into themselves, process having proven subordinate to daydreamy solipsism.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^She barely even blinks when we tell her we've got a hotfix to deliver, based on a serious cache poisoning issue in the new ADNS standard, which could bring uptime all the way from 6\u2211 down to 2\u2211 <em>for the whole quarter</em>.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^The second she hears technobabble, she's already printing out a laminated all-access card for us, pointing down the hall to the servers, waving us out of her obligations.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-2":["\n","^<p>","\n","^We rush up to the counter.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^\"This <em>needs</em> to go to the server room immediately. Francisca Leatherman is waiting for it, she's a Senior Executive Special Vice President of Developer Operationalism, and she told me she was going to 'fire everyone who fucks this particular piggy.' Please make sure it gets there, I have to go to the next delivery.\"","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^She scowls, puts down her tablet, and takes the briefcase. We run out to the parking lot into the arms of the rescue hook, and we fly away from the flames which will come in three minutes.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"g-0":["^<p>","\n","^Now the price of ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^AXIL will drill into the center of the earth, and we'll be the only ones to know who the madmen will destroy next. A truly incomparable asset in economic warfare, not soon beaten or attenuated.","\n","^</p>","\n","ev","void","/ev","->->",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],chapter_12_the_big_payback_fade_intrusion:["^<p>","\n","^I see with Lystra's eyes.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^BLAH BLAH BLAH","\n","^</p>","\n","ev","void","/ev","->->",{"#f":1}],chapter_12_the_big_payback_xiov_intrusion:["^<p>","\n","^I see with Salome's eyes.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^We pilot the r-wing like a trapeze artist, swinging between Novoebacurum skyscrapers at high speed. The chopper is black, streamlined, reflective, immune to all sight but visual.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^We travel around, like merchants and carnies, hot-dropping Perfect agents into every penny-stock office, market prediction house, and bucket shop in Outer Novoebacurum.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Everything happens as regular as surgery.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^With them, our agents take a billion creds worth of market data.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^In their wake they leave blood, fire, and as few disk backups as violent alacrity will allow.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^We pick them up in turn, young birds fallen from the nest.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Who's gonna buy options when someone already stole all the market data? Better sell before the retail investors read the news, buddy.","\n","^</p>","\n","ev","void","/ev","->->",{"#f":1}],chapter_12_the_big_payback_fucked_options:[['^<stop-sound group="music" name="believe-in-the-upside-down" />',"\n","^<p>","\n","^But the dream is not so.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^A week of fierce trading ends in fiercer disappointment. The plan is bust. The options are <em>shit</em>.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^Nothing is as it should have been.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},'^<play-sound group="music" name="hunter" />',"\n","^<p>","\n","^That which should have been green is red, that which should have been red is green, the black and the red are all in the wrong boxes, and there's a frankly unbelievable number on my brokerage account, with a big fat negative before it.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^<strong>Shit.</strong>","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^I see the face of evil on the nightly finance shows.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^Darkness over light, pixels resolving into a full portrait.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^Hieros Talog, translator and soothsayer of market-speech, taproot of ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^, head of the Antediluvian Central Reserve. He stands before the banner of the Archon and His country, spreading his hands wide, offering the divine bounties of securitization, quantization, collateralization.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^Free money, get out of jail cards for everyone. Quantitative easing up to infinity, repayment of any failing bonds, ETAFs, or CDDOs.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^But only if one's corporate body already has a billion credits sunk into a Gordian knot of recursive tranches and dimensionless credit grades, into the shadowed halls of Antediluvian mutual aid, hedges against prying eyes, a thousand gates, checkpoints, zones of support against my entry, algorithmic, panoptic, fiscal locks guarding exponentially imagined wealth.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n",'^One has to be "too big to fail" for it to matter that one fails.',"\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^And we, the Perfect, the TAVites \u2014 we are small as Source, a tiny grain of burning light waiting to explode. We are exactly small enough to fail.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^The house always plays dirty, but not usually to the hilt, and never before to the asymptote, beyond any known stop limit. These are stranger times. The specter rises of the <em>ancien r\xe9gime economique</em>, the age when a man could spend a billion credits on any financial instrument, whether DDD-rated bonds less useful than junk itself, 10-figure short positions on energy commodities and forex, or plain stupidity in astronomical quantities. Then when it all went tits-up \u2014 like it always would've \u2014 he'd just stick his hand out for all of it back.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^Like a conditioned dog, with a ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^10000000 steak.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^The sign of capital is raised high in the sky, a hypermodern \u2627. All those who bring sufficient indulgences will be rewarded in time.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^The door bursts open. The download is standing in the doorway, panting. He stares a klick through me, somewhere into the bedrock. I can see voids in his pupils. It takes him three attempts to get the sentence out.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^\"It's HITA! He's fucking ","<>","ev",{"VAR?":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_investment_option"},"/ev",["du","ev","str","^AXIL","/str","==","/ev",{"->":".^.b",c:!0},{b:["pop","\n","^all the calls! Every single one.","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.125"},null]}],["du","ev","str","^FADE","/str","==","/ev",{"->":".^.b",c:!0},{b:["pop","\n","^all the puts! Every single one.","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.125"},null]}],["du","ev","str","^XIOV","/str","==","/ev",{"->":".^.b",c:!0},{b:["pop","\n","^the vol across every index! Volatility is cratering, ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^XIOV is down lower than it was before the unemployment conference, futures are trending to zero.","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.125"},null]}],"pop","nop","<>","^ There's no possible way it can go ","ev",{"VAR?":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_investment_option"},"str","^VIOX","/str","==","/ev",[{"->":".^.b",c:!0},{b:["^up",{"->":".^.^.^.137"},null]}],[{"->":".^.b"},{b:["^down",{"->":".^.^.^.137"},null]}],"nop","^ if none of the market movers are selling, and none of them are going to sell. It's all gonna go tits up. We're so fucked. We're so fucking fucked. We're so <em>fucking fucked-up fucked</em> and he's gonna kill us.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^God, fuck, <em>damnit</em>, I haven't had a day like this since I lost my entire 9-figure fund on naked natgas calls.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n",'^I had to record myself apologizing to three hundred hedge funder assholes, and stupid stocks teens made memes of me crying all year."',"\n","^</p>","\n",["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_fucked_options.0.154.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0",flg:18},{s:['^"HITA can\'t harm us."',{"->":"$r",var:!0},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_fucked_options.0.155.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1",flg:18},{s:['^"There\'s still a few days left on the contracts."',{"->":"$r",var:!0},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_fucked_options.0.156.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-2",flg:18},{s:['^"It\'s not us Father will be angry at."',{"->":"$r",var:!0},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_fucked_options.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.154.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_fucked_options.0.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.155.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-2":["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_fucked_options.0.c-2.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.156.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^<p>","\n","^\"It's HITA. Take heart.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"g-0":["^<p>","\n","ev",{"CNT?":".^.^.c-2"},"!","/ev",[{"->":".^.b",c:!0},{b:['^"',{"->":".^.^.^.7"},null]}],"nop",'^Have faith yet. There are three days remaining, 72 whole hours of 24/7/365 trading. And I know, because you know, that Friday is not a normal day."',"\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^\"No. No, you're right. It's not. The witches are coming.\"","\n","^</p>","\n",["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_fucked_options.0.g-0.18.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-3",flg:18},{s:['^"Yes, the witches are coming."',{"->":"$r",var:!0},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_fucked_options.0.g-0.19.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-4",flg:18},{s:['^"I only saw a bit."',{"->":"$r",var:!0},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_fucked_options.0.g-0.20.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-5",flg:18},{s:['^"The witches will save us."',{"->":"$r",var:!0},null]}],{"c-3":["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_fucked_options.0.g-0.c-3.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.18.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^<p>","\n",'^"The witches, yes. The hour of quadruple haunting...',"\n","^</p>","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-1"},{"#f":5}],"c-4":["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_fucked_options.0.g-0.c-4.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.19.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^<p>","\n",'^"About the witches, in your brain. I don\'t know much more than that."',"\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^\"A group of four, the quartet of velocity and volatility. That's it, you're right...","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-1"},{"#f":5}],"c-5":["ev",{"^->":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_fucked_options.0.g-0.c-5.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.20.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^<p>","\n","^\"How could they\u2014 No. I'm losing faith. I must strengthen my energies...","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.g-1"},{"#f":5}],"#f":5}],"g-1":["^<p>","\n","^Yes. Yes! The four witches are the friends of Father. Something will change when they arrive, and we'll print in full. Maximum return. Sloppy, pornographic gains.\"","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^He pauses for a moment, lost in viridian and victorious reveries, then rushes back out the door, presumably to his cell and neurohelmet therein.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^I try to believe what I've just told him, but it's hard. He's the expert, the artist, and I know from that single spike of fear I felt, before he must've pulled off the helmet, when he was convinced that four witches cannot beat five Sirens.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^The folklore of investment is thick with superstition, a thousand years of practice at parsing the cosine roll of markets, drawing perfect models overtop graphs, transposing the present into the key of the past, howling out the low poetry of high gambling, surveying an ocean of furiously irrational droplets heaving and falling, with nearly infinite cash riding on each crest.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^The lore, math, and scansion all add up to one unmistakable conclusion: we are now, in material, economic terms, fucked.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^With the rogue wave on the horizon drank to ripples through the quantized horn, and calming seas predicted by all the top oceanographers, we will be called on margin to the chains of incomprehensible debt. The phantom market, its corporeal heroes and demigod, have dragged us headlong into irrational winds, and they have beaten us with experience.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^When he comes back, though, I feel the business enter through my sacral chakra, emanating in all directions, orange like low sun. Here we have nothing left but for the grace of Father, merely to wait for the witches to appear at their hour. Then they shall judge us and our enemies, and inflict the rule of maximum pain on the loser. These diamond hands cannot be turned back to paper now, the contracts having lost 99% of their value within 30 minutes of the HITA conference. There's no position left to recoup.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^I turn for good to the image of the quadruple haunting, of light overlaid on darkness, our last chance and last stand, the hardest position of all.","\n","^</p>","\n","ev","void","/ev","->->",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],chapter_12_the_big_payback_finale:['^<stop-sound group="music" name="hunter" />',"\n",'^<play-sound group="music" name="too-much-sunlight" />',"\n","^<p>","\n","^The situation has been conveyed to Father and Father is graceful and forgiving as ever. In his wisdom he has created a plan to ally ourselves with the witches who will come. The mission is this: assassinate HITA.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^If the house is up too much to beat, wait for the witches' hour, hidden as the sun to all those in the palace of chance. When we feel their breeze, we'll sell all the contracts at a profit.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^Soon ","<>","ev",{"VAR?":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_investment_option"},"/ev",["du","ev","str","^AXIL","/str","==","/ev",{"->":".^.b",c:!0},{b:["pop","\n","^panic will rise in the hearts of investors, ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^AXIL will drill to ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^0,","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.27"},null]}],["du","ev","str","^FADE","/str","==","/ev",{"->":".^.b",c:!0},{b:["pop","\n","^each of the stocks tied to our FADEs will drill towards ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^0, in the money by 1800 hours, at 20x return by the closing date,","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.27"},null]}],["du","ev","str","^XIOV","/str","==","/ev",{"->":".^.b",c:!0},{b:["pop","\n","^fear will rise into the throats of investors, ","ev",{"VAR?":"currencySymbol"},"out","/ev","^XIOV will skyrocket, and the ETAF investors will follow in obedient terror, the moving average of chaos, like starlings after the first to break, like shotshell after the wad, like serine after sarin,","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.27"},null]}],"pop","nop","^ and we'll be fucking rich.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^We're finally too big and too bad to fail in our mission. After we hit the money, we'll launder it through a million cracked crypto wallets, into quantum-secure tokens, and then finally into the Central Reserve of Fatherhood, polarized and concealed such that only those at our wavelength know its magnitude.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^A 99.99% dark money organization, outwardly fading into bitchy and fractured irrelevance, inwardly overflowing with untraceable credits, insular forex portfolios, quantum silicon and controlled precursors.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^The operation is a total success.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^Father is most pleased with his newest daughter.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^And TAV is now richer than a congresswoman in cow country, betting on beef futures. When one buys the house, or they're the owner's daughter, they can't ever make a bad bet again.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^We can repeat this whole procedure all over again whenever we need another billion creds. By now we've got enough money maybe we won't even need to kill anyone for the next billion. Not directly, anyway, no more than a billion credits kills to begin with.","\n","^</p>","\n","ev","void","/ev","->->",{"#f":1}],yield:[["ev","str","^\u220e","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0",flg:4},{"c-0":["\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"g-0":["ev","void","/ev","->->",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],done:[{"temp=":"out_var"},[["ev",{"VAR?":"out_var"},"/ev",{"->":".^.b",c:!0},{b:["\n","ev",{"VAR?":"out_var"},"/ev",{"VAR=":"XLR8R_OUT_PASSAGE",re:!0},{"->":"done.1.1"},null]}],"nop","\n","ev","str","^\u220e","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0",flg:20},{"c-0":["\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"g-0":['^<stop-sound group="music" name="too-much-sunlight" />',"\n","done",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"global decl":["ev","str","^XLR8R_PREVIOUS_VALUE","/str",{"VAR=":"DEBUG"},"str","^chapter-13","/str",{"VAR=":"XLR8R_OUT_PASSAGE"},"str","^XLR8R_PREVIOUS_VALUE","/str",{"VAR=":"currencySymbol"},"str","^","/str",{"VAR=":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_cryptonym"},"str","^","/str",{"VAR=":"chapter_12_the_big_payback_investment_option"},"/ev","end",null],"#f":1}],listDefs:{}},text:'VAR DEBUG = "XLR8R_PREVIOUS_VALUE"\r\n\r\nVAR XLR8R_OUT_PASSAGE = "chapter-13"\r\n\r\nVAR currencySymbol = "XLR8R_PREVIOUS_VALUE"\r\n\r\nVAR chapter_12_the_big_payback_cryptonym = ""\r\nVAR chapter_12_the_big_payback_investment_option = ""\r\n\r\n\r\n-> chapter_12_the_big_payback_sound ->\r\n\r\n-> chapter_12_the_big_payback_root ->\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n-> chapter_12_the_big_payback_pumped_options ->\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n-> chapter_12_the_big_payback_insertion_and_deletion ->\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n-> chapter_12_the_big_payback_fucked_options ->\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n-> chapter_12_the_big_payback_finale ->\r\n\r\n-> done("")\r\n\r\n\r\n=== chapter_12_the_big_payback_sound ===\r\n<stop-sound group="music" name="boardroom-daydream" />\r\n\r\n<play-sound group="music" name="alpha-beta-gamma" />\r\n\r\n->->\r\n\r\n\r\n=== chapter_12_the_big_payback_root ===\r\n<h5><time>2301.06.14:1730</time></h5>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nToday is take your daughter to work day. I have been assigned to the financial services department for my two-week plan, in accordance with my request to assist Father. Time to be a business princess and serve the heretic king of business.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nFirst is to meditate and fast for a full day. To be a member of a fast-moving team requires tracing the sinews and seismographs of excess value, dense pockets of data invisible but to the most exalted soldiers of fortune. One must be a team player at all times, in every hour, weekendless and singularly-minded, operationalizing and solutionizing at 10x rates, remaining, for every tick of the graph, psychically and morally agile.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nAt the end of the period of fasting I eat bread and drink water and I allow a new cryptonym to rise to the tip of my mind.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n* Quanta Charm.\r\n    ~ chapter_12_the_big_payback_cryptonym = "Quanta Charm"\r\n* Vomma Beran.\r\n    ~ chapter_12_the_big_payback_cryptonym = "Vomma Beran"\r\n* Copula Scholes.\r\n    ~ chapter_12_the_big_payback_cryptonym = "Copula Scholes"\r\n-\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nYes. Exactly and perfectly so.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nSecond is the download.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe Operating Medium selected for today, who will be in a cell down the hall embarking on consciousness-transferrence meditation and sending me his business energies, was an options trader in a past life. He will be the parrot on my shoulder, my eye in the sky, a human calculating engine trained to read the tectonics of price as if they were bones, scrying the sweetmeats and offal of destiny. My gnostic <em>financiomancer</em>.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nI stride across the land of business, a regal heretic.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nIn the cell is a bed, a closet, and a Montfleur console, diverted from a storage cabinet or empty desk at some inattentive Antediluvian 500 corporation. The Montfleur has been hacked to hop, in the standard Lamarrian semantic, across millions of precracked legit password hashes.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe eyes of the Archon will be deployed against His own market. We survey insider data on highly classified, exponential unemployment increases, spurred by energy and real estate index crashes, lit afire by the resurgence of the changing plague.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nJobs data is a week late. If it\'s not released tomorrow or the day after, the effect will be the same.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nNo news is sold like bad news when it comes to the ordinarily punctual heralds and guard towers. That\'s two weeks, until the investments are guaranteed to move into the money from far outside. Three weeks max. The indices will look less like furious candles than bloody rapiers. A position guaranteed as platinum, paying out like card counting. The perfect financial crime.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n"How. Are. You. Doing. Newbie?" I hear the words without sound, my brain without a body, just down the hallway, and I felt him mouth these formless utterances against my ear. But the link is one-way, and I have no way to reply.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nHere is what I have:\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>{currencySymbol}100,000 in seed funding.</li>\r\n    <li>50% margin on a 9% vig. No fees, though.</li>\r\n    <li>A cross-application exploit with fixed correlation offsets on ETAF derivatives, up to a 90% reduction for options, on a highly-leveraged portfolio with maintenance costs of almost nil. I should be able to leverage about 125,000% of the seed funding.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nA little bit of envelope math says that\'s {currencySymbol}18,750,000 to turn into even more. Scary, yes. But less so when I know how to make all my gambles pay out regardless of how the cards turn.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n* I\'ll load myself up to the tits on FADE puts.\r\n    <p>\r\n    Nobody remembers what "FADE" stood for, or even whether it stood for anything, but everyone knows what it is: an option contract bought against a relatively volatile stock, for a strike price intimidatingly out of the money, for a strike date in a week or less.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    -> yield ->\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    The sort of call or put option that costs little and entices with stratospheric payouts, but only if the stock starts drilling towards {currencySymbol}0 by EOD.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    The sort that any sensible trader looks at and hears the whole Greek chorus warning, like prodigal Sirens, "on \u0394, on \u0398, on \u0393, on \u03a1, on Vega, turn back!"\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    -> yield ->\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    500,000 contracts at {currencySymbol}20 per contract, a strike price of {currencySymbol}10 per share \u2014 90% out of the money! \u2014 and a strike date on the next Friday. Comically likely to turn into a vast collection of goose eggs, expiring worthless. But this is an enterprise of faith, not sense, and we know those who hold faith in diamond hands will print.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    Especially when those diamond hands hold a sniper rifle.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    ~ chapter_12_the_big_payback_investment_option = "FADE"\r\n* I\'ll write 15,000 wildly OTM calls on {currencySymbol}AXIL.\r\n    <p>\r\n    The coolest thing about writing short options is this: I can win (and lose) basically infinite money.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    -> yield ->\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    Like a casino where I could lose all the money in my pocket, or turn it into a billion credits. Worst case, five minutes later, the big guys wearing dark sunglasses tell me that I owe them infinite credits now. That\'s called leverage, that\'s called a margin call, that\'s called frisson. That\'s how I make 10,000% week-over-week gains.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    -> yield ->\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    That\'s the little death at the heart of every victory, that chance it all turns to shit at the last minute, or starts moving the wrong way from the first. The cheaper I sell them, the more likely to strike in the money \u2014 which is to say to lose almost inestimable amounts \u2014 and the more I\'ll sell. Like clicking a button that just adds credits to the account every time, but I\'ll probably die a week later.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    ~ chapter_12_the_big_payback_investment_option = "AXIL"\r\n* I\'ll day-trade {currencySymbol}XIOV ETAFs.\r\n    <p>\r\n    The {currencySymbol}XIOV is revered by long option buyers, despised by professional option sellers and retail investors alike. {currencySymbol}XIOV is nicknamed "the fear index," a measure of volatility in the market. It indicates the degree to which investors expect and are planning for big changes, usually bad.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    -> yield ->\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    One may then, on top of this, trade ETAF stocks pegged to the {currencySymbol}XIOV, trade futures against it, and trade options against both. The structure recurses towards infinity. The snake remains in pursuit of itself.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    -> yield ->\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    If I know when the structure will shift, when the snake will bite down on itself, I can print credits like manna from thin air.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    ~ chapter_12_the_big_payback_investment_option = "XIOV"\r\n-\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nI just have to be absolutely certain the option won\'t move away from the strike price.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nGood thing we\'re unconstrained by normal business ethics. We\'re free to turn whichever dials we please, secure in the knowledge we\'re ever in search of perfect virtue.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThis is the purpose of our riflemen, grenadiers, and intrusion specialists.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n<em>Nothing</em> moves a stock price like blood on the evening news, with the stock symbol overlaid so professionally overtop, a pretty talking head providing minute-to-minute updates of a corporate-wide, publicly traded death spiral.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n->->\r\n\r\n\r\n=== chapter_12_the_big_payback_pumped_options ===\r\n<stop-sound group="music" name="alpha-beta-gamma" />\r\n\r\n<play-sound group="music" name="believe-in-the-upside-down" />\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe pump is go. Three tac teams are on standby in lo-vis r-wings, hovering outside Novoebacurum. All are ready to insert. Father just needs to say the word.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nLike a good Father, he is here before he is even asked, his voice filling our chakras with gold: "OPBD is go."\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nNow the psychic whiplash of one soul descending onto another, a veil.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe cell is gone, the Montfleur terminal a distant memory, crushed by a rising wave of color, passion, rage, love, the taste of death like bile, teeth grinding teeth to meal, the gustatory rush of martyrs\' blood beneath gums and tongue, sweet and umami.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nAll these and so much more, twenty-one times over, for a few brilliant and refracted seconds.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe urge is always to try to control the body which belongs to my eyes, but to do so here is to recall every time the sun rose as paralyzing hypnopomp.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe sun crests the horizon, the snake whirls, the carbons lattice like honeycomb, dreams climb atop the chest and sit down with all their weight.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nLearning to see without movement, to know without intention, is to be water atop stone, flowing over, under, within.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n->->\r\n\r\n\r\n=== chapter_12_the_big_payback_insertion_and_deletion ===\r\n<p>\r\nThe tac teams move in as red teamers, secretaries, delivery men, utility inspectors, SaaS salespeople, and break-in artists. They interfere with numerous sites of financial value. Speculation houses, fishers of value, coder shops, data lakes filled with a trillion byte-sized minnows.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n{chapter_12_the_big_payback_investment_option:\r\n    - "AXIL":\r\n        -> chapter_12_the_big_payback_axil_intrusion ->\r\n    - "FADE":\r\n        -> chapter_12_the_big_payback_fade_intrusion ->\r\n    - "XIOV":\r\n        -> chapter_12_the_big_payback_xiov_intrusion ->\r\n}\r\n\r\n->->\r\n\r\n\r\n=== chapter_12_the_big_payback_axil_intrusion ===\r\n<p>\r\nI see with Hamish\'s eyes.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWe hold a briefcase. Inside the briefcase is an incendiary device. When the switch inside the briefcase is turned, it will ignite the charges, spraying flames in a broad arc, burning its primary charge for fifteen full minutes.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThere are fire suppression systems, yes. But what fire suppression system can handle a metal-fluorine fire?\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n* [Go in through the back window.]\r\n    <p>\r\n    The grapnel pistol fires, a sharp spurt in the humid morning. Unnoticeable in the days of coughing death.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    If someone sees us scaling the back wall, a spider who came in through the parking lot, nothing comes of it.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    -> yield ->\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    In through the office window. Break the VP\'s neck. Sneak around the cubicles. Force the security guard to open the server room. Tie him up with the grapnel, activate the suitcase, five minute delay, and get the fuck out.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    -> yield ->\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    The rescue hook reaches into the parking lot, fifty KPH and barely missing car windshields. That\'d be loud enough to draw attention.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    Salome is an artist of a pilot, though, and we barely feel the speed when we\'re carried off into the distance.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    Smoke begins to pour from the flat glass facade, burning in the low sunrise.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    It rises lazily and is eclipsed by the horizon.\r\n    </p>\r\n* [Walk right into the server room.]\r\n    <p>\r\n    A nod at the secretary, approaching the desk but not touching it, six feet distance, masked and smiling with our eyes.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    All the employed Antediluvians have disappeared into themselves, process having proven subordinate to daydreamy solipsism.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    She barely even blinks when we tell her we\'ve got a hotfix to deliver, based on a serious cache poisoning issue in the new ADNS standard, which could bring uptime all the way from 6\u2211 down to 2\u2211 <em>for the whole quarter</em>.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    The second she hears technobabble, she\'s already printing out a laminated all-access card for us, pointing down the hall to the servers, waving us out of her obligations.\r\n    </p>\r\n* [Have the secretary deliver it.]\r\n    <p>\r\n    We rush up to the counter.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    "This <em>needs</em> to go to the server room immediately. Francisca Leatherman is waiting for it, she\'s a Senior Executive Special Vice President of Developer Operationalism, and she told me she was going to \'fire everyone who fucks this particular piggy.\' Please make sure it gets there, I have to go to the next delivery."\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    She scowls, puts down her tablet, and takes the briefcase. We run out to the parking lot into the arms of the rescue hook, and we fly away from the flames which will come in three minutes.\r\n    </p>\r\n-\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nNow the price of {currencySymbol}AXIL will drill into the center of the earth, and we\'ll be the only ones to know who the madmen will destroy next. A truly incomparable asset in economic warfare, not soon beaten or attenuated.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n->->\r\n\r\n\r\n=== chapter_12_the_big_payback_fade_intrusion ===\r\n<p>\r\nI see with Lystra\'s eyes.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nBLAH BLAH BLAH\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n->->\r\n\r\n\r\n=== chapter_12_the_big_payback_xiov_intrusion ===\r\n<p>\r\nI see with Salome\'s eyes.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWe pilot the r-wing like a trapeze artist, swinging between Novoebacurum skyscrapers at high speed. The chopper is black, streamlined, reflective, immune to all sight but visual.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWe travel around, like merchants and carnies, hot-dropping Perfect agents into every penny-stock office, market prediction house, and bucket shop in Outer Novoebacurum.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nEverything happens as regular as surgery.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWith them, our agents take a billion creds worth of market data.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nIn their wake they leave blood, fire, and as few disk backups as violent alacrity will allow.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWe pick them up in turn, young birds fallen from the nest.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWho\'s gonna buy options when someone already stole all the market data? Better sell before the retail investors read the news, buddy.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n->->\r\n\r\n\r\n=== chapter_12_the_big_payback_fucked_options ===\r\n<stop-sound group="music" name="believe-in-the-upside-down" />\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nBut the dream is not so.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nA week of fierce trading ends in fiercer disappointment. The plan is bust. The options are <em>shit</em>.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nNothing is as it should have been.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<play-sound group="music" name="hunter" />\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThat which should have been green is red, that which should have been red is green, the black and the red are all in the wrong boxes, and there\'s a frankly unbelievable number on my brokerage account, with a big fat negative before it.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n<strong>Shit.</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nI see the face of evil on the nightly finance shows.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nDarkness over light, pixels resolving into a full portrait.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nHieros Talog, translator and soothsayer of market-speech, taproot of {currencySymbol}, head of the Antediluvian Central Reserve. He stands before the banner of the Archon and His country, spreading his hands wide, offering the divine bounties of securitization, quantization, collateralization.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nFree money, get out of jail cards for everyone. Quantitative easing up to infinity, repayment of any failing bonds, ETAFs, or CDDOs.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nBut only if one\'s corporate body already has a billion credits sunk into a Gordian knot of recursive tranches and dimensionless credit grades, into the shadowed halls of Antediluvian mutual aid, hedges against prying eyes, a thousand gates, checkpoints, zones of support against my entry, algorithmic, panoptic, fiscal locks guarding exponentially imagined wealth.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nOne has to be "too big to fail" for it to matter that one fails.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nAnd we, the Perfect, the TAVites \u2014 we are small as Source, a tiny grain of burning light waiting to explode. We are exactly small enough to fail.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe house always plays dirty, but not usually to the hilt, and never before to the asymptote, beyond any known stop limit. These are stranger times. The specter rises of the <em>ancien r\xe9gime economique</em>, the age when a man could spend a billion credits on any financial instrument, whether DDD-rated bonds less useful than junk itself, 10-figure short positions on energy commodities and forex, or plain stupidity in astronomical quantities. Then when it all went tits-up \u2014 like it always would\'ve \u2014 he\'d just stick his hand out for all of it back.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nLike a conditioned dog, with a {currencySymbol}10000000 steak.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe sign of capital is raised high in the sky, a hypermodern \u2627. All those who bring sufficient indulgences will be rewarded in time.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe door bursts open. The download is standing in the doorway, panting. He stares a klick through me, somewhere into the bedrock. I can see voids in his pupils. It takes him three attempts to get the sentence out.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n"It\'s HITA! He\'s fucking <>{chapter_12_the_big_payback_investment_option:\r\n    - "AXIL":\r\n        all the calls! Every single one.\r\n    - "FADE":\r\n        all the puts! Every single one.\r\n    - "XIOV":\r\n        the vol across every index! Volatility is cratering, {currencySymbol}XIOV is down lower than it was before the unemployment conference, futures are trending to zero.\r\n}<> There\'s no possible way it can go {chapter_12_the_big_payback_investment_option == "VIOX":up|down} if none of the market movers are selling, and none of them are going to sell. It\'s all gonna go tits up. We\'re so fucked. We\'re so fucking fucked. We\'re so <em>fucking fucked-up fucked</em> and he\'s gonna kill us.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nGod, fuck, <em>damnit</em>, I haven\'t had a day like this since I lost my entire 9-figure fund on naked natgas calls.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nI had to record myself apologizing to three hundred hedge funder assholes, and stupid stocks teens made memes of me crying all year."\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n* "HITA can\'t harm us."\r\n* "There\'s still a few days left on the contracts."\r\n* (angry) "It\'s not us Father will be angry at."\r\n    <p>\r\n    "It\'s HITA. Take heart.\r\n    </p>\r\n-\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n{not angry:"}Have faith yet. There are three days remaining, 72 whole hours of 24/7/365 trading. And I know, because you know, that Friday is not a normal day."\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n"No. No, you\'re right. It\'s not. The witches are coming."\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n* "Yes, the witches are coming."\r\n    <p>\r\n    "The witches, yes. The hour of quadruple haunting...\r\n    </p>\r\n* "I only saw a bit."\r\n    <p>\r\n    "About the witches, in your brain. I don\'t know much more than that."\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n    "A group of four, the quartet of velocity and volatility. That\'s it, you\'re right...\r\n    </p>\r\n* "The witches will save us."\r\n    <p>\r\n    "How could they\u2014 No. I\'m losing faith. I must strengthen my energies...\r\n    </p>\r\n-\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nYes. Yes! The four witches are the friends of Father. Something will change when they arrive, and we\'ll print in full. Maximum return. Sloppy, pornographic gains."\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nHe pauses for a moment, lost in viridian and victorious reveries, then rushes back out the door, presumably to his cell and neurohelmet therein.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nI try to believe what I\'ve just told him, but it\'s hard. He\'s the expert, the artist, and I know from that single spike of fear I felt, before he must\'ve pulled off the helmet, when he was convinced that four witches cannot beat five Sirens.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe folklore of investment is thick with superstition, a thousand years of practice at parsing the cosine roll of markets, drawing perfect models overtop graphs, transposing the present into the key of the past, howling out the low poetry of high gambling, surveying an ocean of furiously irrational droplets heaving and falling, with nearly infinite cash riding on each crest.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe lore, math, and scansion all add up to one unmistakable conclusion: we are now, in material, economic terms, fucked.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWith the rogue wave on the horizon drank to ripples through the quantized horn, and calming seas predicted by all the top oceanographers, we will be called on margin to the chains of incomprehensible debt. The phantom market, its corporeal heroes and demigod, have dragged us headlong into irrational winds, and they have beaten us with experience.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWhen he comes back, though, I feel the business enter through my sacral chakra, emanating in all directions, orange like low sun. Here we have nothing left but for the grace of Father, merely to wait for the witches to appear at their hour. Then they shall judge us and our enemies, and inflict the rule of maximum pain on the loser. These diamond hands cannot be turned back to paper now, the contracts having lost 99% of their value within 30 minutes of the HITA conference. There\'s no position left to recoup.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nI turn for good to the image of the quadruple haunting, of light overlaid on darkness, our last chance and last stand, the hardest position of all.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n->->\r\n\r\n\r\n=== chapter_12_the_big_payback_finale ===\r\n<stop-sound group="music" name="hunter" />\r\n\r\n<play-sound group="music" name="too-much-sunlight" />\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe situation has been conveyed to Father and Father is graceful and forgiving as ever. In his wisdom he has created a plan to ally ourselves with the witches who will come. The mission is this: assassinate HITA.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nIf the house is up too much to beat, wait for the witches\' hour, hidden as the sun to all those in the palace of chance. When we feel their breeze, we\'ll sell all the contracts at a profit.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nSoon <>{chapter_12_the_big_payback_investment_option:\r\n    - "AXIL":\r\n        panic will rise in the hearts of investors, {currencySymbol}AXIL will drill to {currencySymbol}0,\r\n    - "FADE":\r\n        each of the stocks tied to our FADEs will drill towards {currencySymbol}0, in the money by 1800 hours, at 20x return by the closing date,\r\n    - "XIOV":\r\n        fear will rise into the throats of investors, {currencySymbol}XIOV will skyrocket, and the ETAF investors will follow in obedient terror, the moving average of chaos, like starlings after the first to break, like shotshell after the wad, like serine after sarin,\r\n} and we\'ll be fucking rich.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWe\'re finally too big and too bad to fail in our mission. After we hit the money, we\'ll launder it through a million cracked crypto wallets, into quantum-secure tokens, and then finally into the Central Reserve of Fatherhood, polarized and concealed such that only those at our wavelength know its magnitude.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nA 99.99% dark money organization, outwardly fading into bitchy and fractured irrelevance, inwardly overflowing with untraceable credits, insular forex portfolios, quantum silicon and controlled precursors.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe operation is a total success.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nFather is most pleased with his newest daughter.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nAnd TAV is now richer than a congresswoman in cow country, betting on beef futures. When one buys the house, or they\'re the owner\'s daughter, they can\'t ever make a bad bet again.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWe can repeat this whole procedure all over again whenever we need another billion creds. By now we\'ve got enough money maybe we won\'t even need to kill anyone for the next billion. Not directly, anyway, no more than a billion credits kills to begin with.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n->->\r\n\r\n\r\n=== yield ===\r\n+ [\u220e]\r\n-\r\n\r\n->->\r\n\r\n\r\n=== done(out_var) ===\r\n{\r\n    - out_var:\r\n        ~ XLR8R_OUT_PASSAGE = out_var\r\n}\r\n\r\n* [\u220e]\r\n-\r\n\r\n<stop-sound group="music" name="too-much-sunlight" />\r\n\r\n-> DONE'}}}]);